__NAME__ purpose
specify user tracking log filename
__END__


__NAME__ synopsis
<arg choice='plain'><replaceable>filename</replaceable></arg>
__END__


__NAME__ description
Specify the <emphasis>usertrack</emphasis> log file location. 
</para><para>
User &glos-tracking; can be used in back office administration to summarize
traffic by affiliates or provide other statistics.
__END__

__NAME__ notes
The &IC; daemon must have the permission to create and write to the
specified file, of course.
__END__

__NAME__ example: Setting TrackFile
<programlisting>
TrackFile logs/usertrack
</programlisting>
__END__

